        "content": "<p>You get multiple motives for mutual and nested inductives. These both have more than one motive:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">mutual</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">inductive</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">nil</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">ofB</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">B</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">inductive</span> <span class=\"n\">B</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">mk</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">B</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">#print</span> <span class=\"n\">A.rec</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">inductive</span> <span class=\"n\">Sexpr</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">atom</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">String</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Sexpr</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">ofList</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">List</span> <span class=\"n\">Sexpr</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Sexpr</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">#print</span> <span class=\"n\">Sexpr.rec</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
